# Storybook Assistant Plugin - Environment Configuration

# ===================================
# Required: Claude API Access
# ===================================
# Plugin uses Claude API for intelligent code generation
# Priority: CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN > ANTHROPIC_API_KEY

# Option 1: Claude Code OAuth Token (Preferred)
CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=your_claude_code_token_here

# Option 2: Anthropic API Key (Fallback)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here

# Get token:
# - CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN: Automatically set by Claude Code CLI
# - ANTHROPIC_API_KEY: https://console.anthropic.com/

# ===================================
# Optional: Visual Generation
# ===================================
# Enable AI-powered visual generation (style guides, mockups, diagrams)
# Powered by OpenRouter (Gemini 3 Pro Image / FLUX.2 Pro)

OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_openrouter_api_key_here

# Get API key: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# Cost: ~$0.05-0.15 per image
# Note: Plugin works perfectly without this - visual generation is 100% optional

# ===================================
# Usage
# ===================================
# 1. Copy this file to .env in your project root:
#    cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Fill in your API keys
#
# 3. Restart Claude Code
#
# 4. Run: /setup-storybook
